'''W. Mark Whittlesey''' was an author and game designer. Together with [[Scott Bennie]] he made [[The Lord of the Rings, Vol. I (1990 computer game)|The Lord of the Rings, Vol. I (PC)]],<ref>[http://www.lysator.liu.se/tolkien-games/entry/lotr1.html The Lord of the Rings, Vol. I] at Tolkien Games (retrieved 1 January 2011)</ref> [[The Lord of the Rings, Vol. II: The Two Towers]] and [[J.R.R. Tolkien's The Lord of the Rings, Vol. I (SNES)|The Lord of the Rings, Vol. I (SNES)]].
